423
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:16,280
Bibili muna ako ng ticket.

424
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:17,050
Teka.

425
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:18,660
Pasensya na sa abala, Binibini.

426
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:20,060
Bibili siya ng tiket mamaya.

427
00:26:20,740 --> 00:26:21,940
