469
00:28:47,250 --> 00:28:48,110
Tama na!

470
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:51,530
Tigilan mo na!

471
00:28:55,730 --> 00:28:57,200
Alam kong malapit ka sa kanya.

472
00:28:58,090 --> 00:28:59,920
Ibinahagi niya sa iyo ang lahat.

473
00:29:03,600 --> 00:29:05,600
Pero hindi ganoon talaga gumagana ang pag-ibig.

474
00:29:06,230 --> 00:29:07,900
May sarili kang buhay na dapat mong mabuhay,

475
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:14,450
