maging katulad ni He Xiangyong para lang sa akin.

476
00:29:14,450 --> 00:29:16,420
Nasaktan ko siya dati.

477
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:17,970
Sa pagkakataong ito,

478
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,490
Ayokong may masaktan ulit.

479
00:29:19,490 --> 00:29:20,460
Chen Haowei.

480
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:22,080
Chen Haowei, huwag kang umalis.

481
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:23,000
-Huwag kang umalis!
-Huwag mo akong pigilan!

482
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:23,900
Chen Haowei!

483
00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:28,260
Iniisip mo rin na ako siya, 'di ba?

484
00:29:28,820 --> 00:29:30,680
Bakit hindi mo pagkatiwalaan ang sarili mo,

485
00:29:30,710 --> 00:29:32,120
Chen Haowei?

486
00:29:38,170 --> 00:29:46,530
[Epilogo]

487
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,930
Ilang minuto ka lang nakatulog
at nagsimula ka na magdrowing.

488
00:29:49,930 --> 00:29:51,740
Hindi ba't sinabi ko sa'yo na mag-review ka ng lessons mo?

489
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:53,610
Mamaya ko na gagawin 'yan.

490
00:29:53,970 --> 00:29:55,170
Ano ang iginuguhit mo?

491
00:29:55,490 --> 00:29:56,760
Teka!

492
00:29:57,290 --> 00:29:57,990
Teka!

493
00:30:01,060 --> 00:30:03,110
Nagsasanay ako
sa pagguhit ng portrait nitong mga nakaraang araw.

494
00:30:03,110 --> 00:30:04,210
Pagguhit ng retrato, 'di ba?

495
00:30:04,210 --> 00:30:04,970
Oo.

496
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:07,020
Aalis na ako. Paalam.

497
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,320
Siya si Xiangyong.

498
00:30:09,930 --> 00:30:11,330
Huwag kang sumuko sa pagguhit.

499
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:15,410
Bakit mo bigla-bigla na lang sinasabi 'to ?

500
00:30:15,410 --> 00:30:16,510
Dahil iyon

501
00:30:16,980 --> 00:30:18,580
yung talagang gusto mong gawin.

502
00:30:20,550 --> 00:30:21,880
Gusto kong sundan ang iyong sining

503
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:23,580
magpakailanman at magpakailanman

504
00:30:24,120 --> 00:30:25,920
at maging pinakamalaking tagahanga mo habangbuhay.

505
00:30:57,170 --> 00:31:02,870
[Susunod na Episode]

506
00:30:57,250 --> 00:30:58,620
Dahil gusto niyang nakawin ang tiket ko.

507
00:30:58,620 --> 00:31:00,150
Kung mamamatay ako nang ganito,

508
00:31:00,150 --> 00:31:01,750
Maaalala mo ako magpakailanman.

509
00:31:03,090 --> 00:31:04,890
Kung tatahakin natin ang landas na ito,

510
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,430
tahakin natin ito habang buhay.

511
00:31:10,450 --> 00:31:12,390
Kaligayahang nakamit mula sa isang hiling...

512
00:31:14,190 --> 00:31:15,990
Iniisip ko kung gaano katagal ito tatagal.
